  <brief_title>Combined Determination of sTREM-1, PCT and CD64 in Diagnosing Sepsis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Combined Determination of sTREM-1, PCT and CD64 in Diagnosing Sepsis: a Prospective, Bicentric Study</official_title>
