  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine wether the combined measurement of the soluble form
      of TREM-1, PCT and the determination of neutrophils CD64 expression could diagnose sepsis in
      critically ill patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
